<h2 id="section-top">General Surgery</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=104613">London North West University Healthcare NHS Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContenta65c56424e944cf9aa3e3f5cac9f2895">
</div>
<p>Our general surgery service provides a complete surgical gastroenterology service, including routine general surgery, specialist gastrointestinal surgery, and acute emergency surgery.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.lnwh.nhs.uk/service-finder/service/general-surgery-32/">Visit our website for more information on this service</a>. </p>
<ul class="service-section srv-basic-details">
</ul>
<p> </p></div>
</div>
</div>
